sqlStatements: ALTER TABLE USERS RENAME TO PRE_MIGRATION_TABLE_USERS;
ALTER TABLE PRE_MIGRATION_TABLE_USERS RENAME TO HOUSEHOLDS;

CREATE TABLE NEW_CREATED_TABLE_USERS (
	Name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
	HouseholdID INTEGER NOT NULL,
	Major VARCHAR DEFAULT 'Bachelor of Computing',
	Pet VARCHAR(255),
	USER_ID VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
	FOREIGN KEY (HouseholdID) REFERENCES HOUSEHOLDS(HOUSEHOLD_ID) ON UPDATE CASCADE ON DELETE CASCADE);
INSERT INTO NEW_CREATED_TABLE_USERS (Pet,Name,HouseholdID,Major) SELECT Pets,Name,HouseholdID,Major FROM SYSTEM_USERS;
ALTER TABLE NEW_CREATED_TABLE_USERS RENAME TO SYSTEM_USERS;
